'''Al Naft Stadium''', is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Baghdad]], [[Iraq]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home stadium of [[Al Naft]].  The stadium holds 3,000 people.

