{{Infobox football club | clubname = Shakhtyor Tashkömür| image = | fullname = FC Shakhtyor Tashkömür| nickname = | founded = | ground = [[Tashkömür]], [[Kyrgyzstan]]| capacity = | chairman = | manager = | league = [[Kyrgyzstan League]] | season = 1994| position = 13th| }}
'''FC Shakhtyor Tashkömür''' is a [[Kyrgyzstan]]i football club based in [[Tashkömür]], [[Kyrgyzstan]] that played in the top division in Kyrgyzstan, the [[Kyrgyzstan League]].
