The '''Lithuania men's students basketball team''' ([[Lithuanian language|Lithuanian]]: ''Lietuvos studentų vyrų krepšinio rinktinė'') represents [[Lithuania]] at various students competitions.<ref>{{cite web|title=Lietuvos studentų krepšinio lyga|url=https://www.facebook.com/studentukrepsinis/info?tab=page_info|website=Facebook.com|accessdate=22 August 2015}}</ref> Most of the team members plays at the [[Lietuvos studentų krepšinio lyga]], though some of them are members of the professional basketball clubs, such as [[BC Žalgiris|Žalgiris Kaunas]] and [[BC Lietuvos rytas|Lietuvos rytas Vilnius]]. The team won gold medals at the [[Basketball at the 2007 Summer Universiade|2007 Summer Universiade]] and bronze medals at the [[Basketball at the 2011 Summer Universiade|2011 Summer Universiade]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mikalajūnas|first1=Tautvydas|title=Lietuvos studentų krepšinio rinktinei - universiados auksas|url=http://www.lrytas.lt/-11874126241185597771-lietuvos-student%C5%B3-krep%C5%A1inio-rinktinei-universiados-auksas.htm|website=lrytas.lt|accessdate=22 August 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lietuvos studentams – universiados bronza|url=http://www.basketnews.lt/news-41663-lietuvos-studentams-universiados-bronza.html|website=BasketNews.lt|accessdate=22 August 2015}}</ref>

